contracts/compliant_pool is adapted from the "tornado_classic" mixer contract
in https://github.com/yugocabrio/rs-soroban-ultrahonk (MIT licensed), which
provides the Poseidon2 incremental Merkle tree and UltraHonk verifier wiring
this project extends with an ASP allow-list cross-check.
